%p Dear #{@booking.session.organizer.public_display_name},

%p We are thrilled to inform you that we have reserved a spot on #{@booking.start_at.in_time_zone(@booking.session.organizer.timezone).strftime('%d %b %I:%M %p (timezone %Z)')} until #{@booking.end_at.in_time_zone(@booking.session.organizer.timezone).strftime('%d %b %I:%M %p (timezone %Z)')} for your session on #{@booking.session.channel.title} channel with #{@booking.user.public_display_name} and it is now ready in your calendar!

- unless @booking.comment.blank?
  %p Comment from client:
  %p= @booking.comment

%p To ensure a seamless experience, please join the session promptly at #{@booking.session.start_at.in_time_zone(@booking.session.organizer.timezone).strftime('%I:%M %p')} on #{@booking.session.start_at.in_time_zone(@booking.booking_slot.user.timezone).strftime('%e %b')}.
%p We have included a direct links for easy access:
%p
  %a{href: @booking.session.absolute_path} Link to Session page
%p
  %a{href: spa_dashboard_booking_index_url} Link to Dashboard/Booking

%p If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team. We are here to help!

%p Thank you for being a valued member of our platform. We look forward to seeing you at the session and witnessing the incredible experience unfold.

%p
  Best regards,
  %br/
  #{Rails.application.credentials.global[:service_name].capitalize} Team
